px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年轻的时候感觉“无房无债一身轻”，赚多少花多少；但是越往后，身上的担子越重，捆绑住你的事情会越来越多。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img class=\" \" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8DoQ2HTrG9zEskibYA7jsJINJGMMxz2LqFW1kggsGhAkeASyt8tgRK7nUpsBT3jv30xFB9fibLWUDiaw1BLlXTsHw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">作家毛利分享过一个粉丝的故事。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">粉丝的老公是个年薪百万并且有股权分配的技术男，但是生活十分节俭。自己用碎了屏的手机，穿着特别朴素的衣服，除了肯给孩子花钱，其余时候一心扑在工作和存钱上。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年轻时的我很不屑，认为年薪百万了，至于吗？但随着自己也开始步入中年，我开始理解了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(153, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">毕竟<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“一分钱难倒英雄汉”，这种痛，中年人最懂。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">有天早上，我在医院门口的早餐店吃饭。看见一对穿着旧棉袄的夫妻抱着一个孩子从医院里走过来。孩子饿了，想吃小笼包，他们就停下来怯生生地问老板：一笼多少钱？老板说：12块钱一笼。</span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但那个父亲搜遍全身只剩下3块5，他不好意思地掏出一卷皱巴巴的纸币，涨红了脸：“钱给孩子看病都用光了，就剩这几块。拜托您看看，能买几个，给孩子尝一尝。”</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">店家不耐烦地给了他2个小笼包，这个父亲小心翼翼地捧着2个小笼包，一个给了孩子，一个给了妻子。妻子也舍不得吃，让给了孩子吃了。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">然后这个父亲转过头，悄悄地抹掉了眼角的泪。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">成年人的世界里，从来没有“容易”二字。人到中年，你再没有权利，心安理得地做个“穷人”。因为，你身后有家庭、有妻儿，你必须要拼命、给家人提供更好的生活。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><section><section><section><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><img class=\" \" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8DoQ2HTrG9zEskibYA7jsJINJGMMxz2Lqp8Hh5yLvibejJG0ENI6uTxF9Yph7UWINicibheqVJyA4u6qxP5WRSJejA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">中年来临，悄无声息；人到中年，捉襟见肘。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">父母老了，为免子欲孝而亲不待的愧疚，要给父母一个幸福安逸的晚年；孩子还小，父母正是孩子的第一任老师，理应给予孩子更好的教育资源；婚姻工作都要兼顾，要家庭和睦，给无法预料的日子多一些保障……</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们成了家里的顶梁柱，也是家里的钱包。好像我们能做的，只有拼命地赚钱，和咬着牙省钱。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但节俭，并不意味着必须降低自己的生活需求，反而是用智慧提升生活品质。</span></p>'),
(2, '李宗盛唱哭自己：我终于失去了你……', 2, '2018-02-11 13:02:43', '2018-11-20 17:11:32', 0, '<p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于爱情的路啊 我们都曾经走过</span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于爱情的歌啊 我们已听得太多</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于我们的事啊 他们统统都猜错</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于心中的话 心中的话</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">只对你 一个人说</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">《生命中的精灵》，是年轻时心动的受挫。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“二十九年前，在旧金山湾区的山景城我爱上了一个女生，当然，没戏了，离开的时候就产生了这首《生命中的精灵》。”</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年少时多愁善感的李宗盛，在离开的车上，哭了一路。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所有知道我的名字的人呐</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">你们好不好</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">世界时如此的小</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们注定无处可逃</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当我尝尽人情冷暖</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当你决定为了你的理想燃烧</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">生活的压力与生命的尊严</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">哪一个重要</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">《我是一只小小鸟》，唱的是小人物无奈而又卑怯的心境。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">李宗盛专门写给好友赵传，也写给为梦想打拼的头几年，那些“刚刚富起来的，有钱买第一辆车的男人”，也写给那时的自己。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我想我是真的爱你，我是真的爱你</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我全心全意等待着你说愿意</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">也许是我太心急……</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">《我是真的很爱你》，诉尽了爱情的甜蜜。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">李宗盛和林忆莲因《霸王别姬》的主题曲结缘，后来暗生情愫。但那时李宗盛和前妻还没有离婚，只能悄悄写下这首歌，唱出自己与林忆莲缠绵悱恻时的爱。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我终于失去了你</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; 